---
title: Classic Lamb Shepherd's Pie with Cheesy Mashed Potato Topping
description: A hearty hug in a dish! This classic lamb shepherd’s pie is rich, savoury, and topped with golden, cheesy crushed potatoes for the ultimate comfort food fix—nostalgic, satisfying, and seriously delicious.
